</A>
</H3>
<address>
ROP GONGGRIJP
&lt;<A HREF="mailto:rop@neabbs.UUCP ">
rop@neabbs.UUCP 
</A>&gt;
</address>
<i>
Thu Mar 30 02:00:20 1989
