Steve Den Beste
</A><br>
<DT><IMG SRC="/Images/redball.gif" ALT= "o"><A HREF="#subj5">
  Re: UK Defence Software Standard 
</A>
<DD>
<A HREF="#subj5.1">
Mark Moraes
</A><br>
<A HREF="#subj5.2">
 Douglas W. Jones
</A><br>
<DT><IMG SRC="/Images/redball.gif" ALT= "o"><A HREF="#subj6">
  Polling vs. interrupts 
</A>
