<HR><H3><A NAME="subj9.2">
For your amusement [ RISKS summer reruns? ]
</A>
</H3>
<address>
Jim Horning
&lt;<A HREF="mailto:horning@src.dec.com ">
horning@src.dec.com 
</A>&gt;
</address>
<i>
2 Aug 1989 1828-PDT (Wednesday)
</i><PRE>

