<HR><H3><A NAME="subj2.4">
Re: Automatic vehicle systems (<A HREF="/Risks/9.14.html">RISKS-9.14</A>)
</A>
</H3>
<address>
Emily H. Lonsford
&lt;<A HREF="mailto:m19940@mwvm.mitre.org ">
